import * as React from "react";
const SVGComponent = (props) => (
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    xmlnsXlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
    width="800px"
    height="159px"
    {...props}
  >
    <image
      x="0px"
      y="0px"
      width="800px"
      height="159px"
      xlinkHref="data:img/png;base64,"
    />
  </svg>
);
export default SVGComponent;
